headline: EPlus (PLUS) Tops Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: ePlus (PLUS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 27.59% and 4.91%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
